WEBVTT

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:34.336
To attain this control here is a tip:
adopt a healthy lifestyle -- eat well,

00:05:34.360 --> 00:05:38.880
sleep soundly and exercise every day 
for a minimum of 30 minutes,

00:05:38.880 --> 00:05:41.880
until you break into a sweat.

00:05:41.880 --> 00:05:47.896
Other than this every day, do some practice
like meditation to keep your mind calm.

00:05:47.920 --> 00:05:50.016
Even if it is just for two minutes.

00:05:50.040 --> 00:05:52.760
I am sure that you already know that

00:05:52.760 --> 00:05:56.990
staying healthy is very important
to stay happy.

00:05:57.490 --> 00:06:01.030
What you probably did not know is that